@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@contentType = application/json
@productId = cmmai4xvd0001vkkg44bchr17
@reservationId = REPLACE_WITH_RESERVATION_CUID

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics

### DB Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/db

### Create Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "sku": "SKU-002",
  "name": "XBOX_1",
  "description": "Drop item Nber2",
  "stock": 10
}

### List Products (pagination/filter/sort)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=1&limit=20&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc&name=Item&minStock=0&maxStock=100

### Reserve
POST {{baseUrl}}/reserve
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "quantity": 2
}

### Checkout
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkout
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "reservationId": "{{reservationId}}"
}

### List Reservations
GET {{baseUrl}}/reservations?page=1&limit=20&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc&status=ACTIVE&productId={{productId}}

### List Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?page=1&limit=20&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc&status=CONFIRMED

### List Inventory Logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory-logs?page=1&limit=20&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc&productId={{productId}}&eventType=RESERVE
